name: .DA0 File Extension
summary: Learn about .DA0 files and view a list of programs that open them.

description: Backup of the Registry database used by Windows; contains a copy of original registry files; for example, system.da0 is the backup file for system.dat.

content: DA0 files may be used to replace corrupt registry files. They are not meant to be opened or edited by the user.
